<h4><a href="https://www.cnbeta.com/articles/tech/1017865.htm">苹果市值达到 2 万亿美元</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1359926" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/tim-cook-wwdc-2019-1500x1000-1.jpg" alt="" width="1500" height="1000" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/tim-cook-wwdc-2019-1500x1000-1.jpg 1500w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/tim-cook-wwdc-2019-1500x1000-1-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/tim-cook-wwdc-2019-1500x1000-1-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/tim-cook-wwdc-2019-1500x1000-1-1024x683.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1500px) 100vw, 1500px" /></p>
<p>新浪科技消息，苹果股价昨晚创下新高，市值一度突破两万亿美元。今年以来，苹果股价已累计上涨超 60%。苹果花了 42 年时间才达到 1 万亿美元的价值，仅仅花了两年时间便达到了 2 万亿美元。</p>
<p>历史上首家突破 2 万亿美元市值的公司是沙特阿美，在去年上市初期创造了这个市值记录。苹果市值在上月超过沙特阿美，成为全球市值最高的公司。</p>
<h4><a href="https://www.sohu.com/a/413945292_114760">黑莓 5G 手机 2021 年上市，配备物理键盘</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1359927" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/137319-phones-news-feature-the-history-of-blackberry-the-best-blackberry-phones-that-changed-the-world-image1-6yn4jlwi0b.jpg" alt="" width="1200" height="800" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/137319-phones-news-feature-the-history-of-blackberry-the-best-blackberry-phones-that-changed-the-world-image1-6yn4jlwi0b.jpg 1200w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/137319-phones-news-feature-the-history-of-blackberry-the-best-blackberry-phones-that-changed-the-world-image1-6yn4jlwi0b-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/137319-phones-news-feature-the-history-of-blackberry-the-best-blackberry-phones-that-changed-the-world-image1-6yn4jlwi0b-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/137319-phones-news-feature-the-history-of-blackberry-the-best-blackberry-phones-that-changed-the-world-image1-6yn4jlwi0b-1024x683.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" /></p>
<p>快科技消息，黑莓和 TCL 始于 2016 年的手机合作将于本月 31 日结束，OnwardMobility 公司将成为黑莓手机的最新合作方，并将和富士康旗下的 FIH 富智康合作。</p>
<p>OnwardMobility 宣布，他们将于 2021 年推出一款黑莓 5G 手机，配备物理键盘，主攻欧洲及北美市场。</p>
<h4><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1293888" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/keji.png" alt="" width="1715" height="300" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/keji.png 1715w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/keji-360x63.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/keji-768x134.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/keji-1024x179.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1715px) 100vw, 1715px" /></h4>
<h4><a href="https://www.cnbeta.com/articles/tech/1017857.htm">听钥匙进锁声就能复制钥匙？</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1359928" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/How-To-Open-a-Lock-Without-a-Key.jpg" alt="" width="1920" height="1080" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/How-To-Open-a-Lock-Without-a-Key.jpg 1920w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/How-To-Open-a-Lock-Without-a-Key-360x203.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/How-To-Open-a-Lock-Without-a-Key-768x432.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/How-To-Open-a-Lock-Without-a-Key-1024x576.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px" /></p>
<p>cnBeta 消息，研究人员最近研发出一种名为 SpiKey 的系统，可通过分析处理钥匙滑入锁中时发出的一系列可听的金属点击声破解出门锁的设计，并用 3D 打印出钥匙的副本。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1359929" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/9b27a6844c05c77.jpg" alt="" width="1280" height="720" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/9b27a6844c05c77.jpg 1280w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/9b27a6844c05c77-360x203.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/9b27a6844c05c77-768x432.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/9b27a6844c05c77-1024x576.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px" /></p>
<p>该系统不需要高端麦克风，只要离锁足够近，智能手机或智能门铃都能记录这些声音。研究人员指出，一种可能可破坏这种分析方式是，用非恒定的速度将钥匙插入锁中。</p>
<h4><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/status/4539574883459386?">ThinkPad 预告首款折叠屏笔记本 ThinkPad X1 Fold</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1359930" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/606d7442ly1ghvw2y32bxj20u01hcjyn.jpg" alt="" width="1080" height="1920" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/606d7442ly1ghvw2y32bxj20u01hcjyn.jpg 1080w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/606d7442ly1ghvw2y32bxj20u01hcjyn-360x640.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/606d7442ly1ghvw2y32bxj20u01hcjyn-768x1365.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/606d7442ly1ghvw2y32bxj20u01hcjyn-576x1024.jpg 576w" sizes="(max-width: 1080px) 100vw, 1080px" /></p>
