<h4>国行《健身环大冒险》将于 9 月 3 日发售</h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1359931" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/yingtang.jpg" alt="" width="1920" height="1080" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/yingtang.jpg 1920w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/yingtang-360x203.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/yingtang-768x432.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/yingtang-1024x576.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px" /></p>
